ZH: 请遵守校园规定。
EN: Please adhere to the campus regulations.

ZH: 这是一个不容违背的法律，在这个国家必须遵守。
EN: This is a law that must not be violated and must be adhered to in this country.

ZH: 作为一名学生，必须遵守学校的规章制度。
EN: As a student, one must adhere to the school's rules and regulations.

ZH: 在这个公司工作，必须遵守公司的行为准则。
EN: Working in this company requires adherence to the company's code of conduct.

ZH: 请记住遵守交通规则，保障自己和他人的安全。
EN: Please remember to adhere to traffic rules to ensure your safety and that of others.

ZH: 他一向很守规矩，遵守家规。
EN: He has always been very well-behaved and adheres to the household rules.

ZH: 作为一名公民，我们必须遵守国家法律。
EN: As citizens, we must adhere to the laws of the country.

ZH: 警察会要求司机遵守交通规则。
EN: The police will ask drivers to adhere to traffic rules.

ZH: 她是一个很守规矩的人，总是遵守规则。
EN: She is a very well-behaved person who always follows the rules.

ZH: 遵守规定是每个人的责任，不能有丝毫的忽略。
EN: Adhering to regulations is everyone's responsibility and cannot be ignored in the slightest.

ZH: 在这个社会中，我们必须遵守道德准则。
EN: In this society, we must adhere to moral standards.

ZH: 在这家公司，员工必须遵守公司的内部规定。
EN: In this company, employees must adhere to the company's internal regulations.

ZH: 无论在什么情况下，我们都应该遵守法律。
EN: In whatever situation, we should always abide by the law.

ZH: 我们必须遵守大自然的规律，保护环境。
EN: We must adhere to the laws of nature and protect the environment.

ZH: 在学校里，我们要遵守老师的教导。
EN: In school, we should follow the guidance of our teachers.

ZH: 希望每个人都能够严格遵守这条规则。
EN: I hope everyone can strictly adhere to this rule.

ZH: 遵守约定是举办一个成功活动的关键。
EN: Adhering to agreements is the key to holding a successful event.

ZH: 无论何时，我们都必须遵守公司的政策。
EN: Whenever it is, we must adhere to the company's policies.

ZH: 他是一个很守规矩的孩子，总是遵守规则。
EN: He is a very well-behaved child who always follows the rules.

ZH: 参加这个活动必须遵守相关的规定。
EN: Participation in this activity must adhere to the relevant regulations.
